Net/FTP/blat version 0.02
===========================

Adds two methods, slurp and blat, to Net::FTP.  Slurp and blat
are like get and put except they work with scalar variables instead of
local files.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Net::FTP

